## 0x05 api.bountypay.h1ctf.com
Finally having an `X-Token` I went back to `api.bountypay.h1ctf.com` to see if I can interact directly (without the app.bountypay.h1ctf.com proxy) and this was the case.

Guess what? More recon!

I fired again `dirsearch` with the `X-Token` header which showed me a nice API endpoint: `/api/staff`:

