I thought about my bruteforce options to find a valid `staff_id`, but I quickly realized that sending `36^10` is not a good idea ðŸ™„.

While taking a break on Twitter I found the [@BountyPayHQ](https://twitter.com/BountypayHQ) account which follows the [@SandraA76708114](https://twitter.com/SandraA76708114), which has a photo of her `BountyPay` badge.

